cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the Natural Language Processing (NLP) aspect of emojis and their underlying semantics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The study of predicting emojis from text-based messages also involves the analysis of social media data, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper involves the use of predictive models, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
